net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold

Class BridgeMethodResolver.Simple

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold.BridgeMethodResolver.Simple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BridgeMethodResolver
    Enclosing interface:
    BridgeMethodResolver

    public static class BridgeMethodResolver.Simple
extends Object
implements BridgeMethodResolver
    A simple bridge method resolver which applies its resolution by analyzing non-generic types. When a type inherits from a generic type and additionally overloads this method, this resolution might be ambiguous.
